# Usage

<!-- usage -->
```sh-session
$ npm install -g @condohub/cli
$ nr COMMAND
running command...
$ nr (-v|--version|version)
@condohub/cli/1.0.1 darwin-arm64 node-v16.14.0
$ nr --help [COMMAND]
USAGE
  $ nr COMMAND
...
```
